1. How to build native module:
1.1. run "node-gyp configure"
1.2. run "node-gyp build"

2. How to run unit test (mocha)
2.1 run "mocha native-example.test.js"

3. How to run cucumber test
3.1 run "cucumber-js" (test and steps defined in subfolder "features")

4. How to run node app script
4.1 run "node native-example.app.js" 

5. Results
5.1 unit test with Promise failes
5.2. cucumber step with Promise failes
5.3. all tests without Promise (mocha and cucumber) passes
5.4. node app with Promise passes